text: The Trump campaign racked up a string of legal losses in its nit-picking challenges to the election outcome, while adding another lawsuit that experts say is either a non-starter or a pointless delaying tactic https://t.co/Nxm3ua9qMp

text:
Some Twitter users have called out attorney John Pierce for trying to “incite violence.”

Asked whether he was actually encouraging people to bear arms to defend Trump, Pierce told The Daily Beast, “Of course not. Just metaphors.” https://t.co/y8LOSJ5HI3
